    "description": "Sally is a new genre of life-simulation game about <strong>community and belonging</strong>. Embark on a grand journey aboard a <strong>magic flying ship</strong> crewed by kids and stewarded by two caring grandmas. Navigate daily life with a diverse array of characters. <strong>Craft, cook, farm, build</strong> and <strong>explore the skies</strong> as you become who you want to be amongst the Sally’s found-family.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165040/extras/b64f27f21005419fc8ad30455f420c2d.poster.avif?t=1748030337\" width=602 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165040/extras/b64f27f21005419fc8ad30455f420c2d.webm?t=1748030337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165040/extras/b64f27f21005419fc8ad30455f420c2d.mp4?t=1748030337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build Lasting Relationships</strong></h2>Get to know your unique crew: the characters are <strong>different in every game</strong> you play! Each of your crewmates has their own life vibrant with <strong>emotions, tastes, interests</strong>, and even <strong>memories</strong>. Develop bonds like <strong>friendships</strong> and <strong>rivalries</strong>. Learn about everyone’s <strong>distinctive personality</strong> and <strong>aspirations</strong>. Watch new connections form aboard the ship, as your crewmates navigate their own relationships.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165040/extras/5c53bb9bf5cbe68a67479baaf0595fa1.poster.avif?t=1748030337\" width=602 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165040/extras/5c53bb9bf5cbe68a67479baaf0595fa1.webm?t=1748030337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165040/extras/5c53bb9bf5cbe68a67479baaf0595fa1.mp4?t=1748030337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Craft, Cook, Farm &amp; Build</strong></h2>An array of <strong>cozy activities</strong> awaits: gather resources on unexplored islands. Cook a comforting meal for your best friend. Take care of animals, build new structures, craft new items, and <strong>improve the Sally</strong> to feel at home.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165040/extras/affc065879fff3c63a6e544fba4131ec.poster.avif?t=1748030337\" width=602 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165040/extras/affc065879fff3c63a6e544fba4131ec.webm?t=1748030337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165040/extras/affc065879fff3c63a6e544fba4131ec.mp4?t=1748030337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Find your Path</strong></h2>Acquire <strong>experience points</strong> by performing tasks and quests, and use them to <strong>unlock new skills</strong>. In what ways will you leave your mark in this community? Choose the <strong>specific role</strong> - or roles - you'd like to enbody amongst the crew.<br><br>It will take a village to lead the Sally to its final destination, and to do so, everyone aboard the ship will have to achieve their <strong>personal aspiration</strong>. Help your crewmates hone their craft and <strong>grow together</strong> to reach your full potential!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165040/extras/d24906244c3d51537988e19196c73bf9.poster.avif?t=1748030337\" width=602 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165040/extras/d24906244c3d51537988e19196c73bf9.webm?t=1748030337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165040/extras/d24906244c3d51537988e19196c73bf9.mp4?t=1748030337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore a Rich New World</strong></h2>The sky is filled with <strong>floating islands</strong> awaiting to be discovered. These eco-systems have different <strong>seasons, resources, animals</strong> and <strong>inhabitants</strong>. Journey through ever-changing landscapes and explore to your heart's content. There’s solace to be found in every task, and <strong>no time limit</strong>. Experience the beauty of Sally’s world at your own pace.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165040/extras/0308285c7158e88dc2a1e29fe78f424c.avif?t=1748030337\" width=602 height=169 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Customize your experience</strong></h2>Select your preferred body type, facial features, skin color, hair color and style, eye color, pronouns, clothes, accessories, and more! Many <strong>customization elements</strong> are available so you can truly <strong>recognize yourself</strong> in your character.<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165040/extras/1edb1f81b551e97069f2b3daee111875.poster.avif?t=1748030337\" width=602 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165040/extras/1edb1f81b551e97069f2b3daee111875.webm?t=1748030337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165040/extras/1edb1f81b551e97069f2b3daee111875.mp4?t=1748030337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
